Program: Discovery
Title: Megalithic expedition in Spain
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxp7
Last Broadcast Date: 16 August 2000
Report from an archaeological dig at the Picos de Europa National Park, Cantabria, Northern Spain to uncover Megalithic shrines. The programme follows scientists as they attempt to explore the secrets of a society, and a world, that existed over 6,000 years ago.